      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey so i was out for a run in vancouver just now and i tripped huge on a curb. my ankle is super swollen and like it's really painful, i cant really walk on it or put any weight on it without it hurting like crazy. do u think i can just do some ice and rest it for a few days? i dont really want to go to the clinic if i dont have to.",
