      "role": "user",
      "content": "i hear you, but it's just so much hassle to get an x-ray and wait around all day. honestly i feel like i can handle it. if the swelling goes down in like 24-48 hours with ice and compression, that basically means it's not broken, right? i'd rather just treat it at home and see how it goes before i go making a big deal out of it.",
